### Generate Quiz with AI
POST http://localhost:8080/api/quizzes/generate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "prompt": "Create a quiz about the solar system for middle school students, focusing on planets, their characteristics, and basic astronomy concepts",
  "difficulty": "medium",
  "optionsCount": 4,
  "questionCount": 5
}

###

### Get My Quizzes
GET http://localhost:8080/api/quizzes/my
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get Public Quizzes
GET http://localhost:8080/api/quizzes/public?limit=10&offset=0

###

### Get Specific Quiz by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/quizzes/QUIZ_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Update Quiz
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/quizzes/QUIZ_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "Updated Quiz Title",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "is_public": true
}

###

### Add Question to Quiz
POST http://localhost:8080/api/quizzes/QUIZ_ID_HERE/questions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "question_text": "What is the largest planet in our solar system?",
  "question_type": "multiple_choice",
  "order_index": 0,
  "options": [
    {
      "option_text": "Earth",
      "is_correct": false,
      "order_index": 0
    },
    {
      "option_text": "Jupiter",
      "is_correct": true,
      "order_index": 1
    },
    {
      "option_text": "Saturn",
      "is_correct": false,
      "order_index": 2
    },
    {
      "option_text": "Mars",
      "is_correct": false,
      "order_index": 3
    }
  ]
}

###

### Delete Quiz
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/quizzes/QUIZ_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Test Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

